      "description": "Currently\u00a0identifying error sources can be quite difficult, as they are written into an unstructured string \"diagnostics\" field. This is present in container statuses returned to the RM and in application attempts in the RM. These errors are difficult to classify without hard-coding\u00a0diagnostic string searches.\r\n\r\nThis Jira aims to add a structured error field in NM and RM that preserves failure information and source component to enable faster and clearer error diagnosis\r\n\r\n\u00a0",
